      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "今日から、星見プロでお世話になります\nⅢXの、kanaです！！",
      "startTime": 3.6670611382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、kana達に大恥かかせたやつらの事務所に\n来ることになるとは、思いませんでしたけど～",
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（ⅢXは、I-UNITYの決勝でサニピとぶつかって）\n（……激戦の末に、敗退した）",
      "startTime": 17.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（その負けた相手と同じ事務所に入ることになったら）\n（まぁ、複雑だよな）",
      "startTime": 24.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、こうなったらしゃーないし",
      "startTime": 26.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "別にフリーでアイドル続けても良かったんだけどさ～\nやっぱ、使えるやつがいた方が楽だもんね",
      "startTime": 33.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "ってことで\n今日からよろしくね、{user}！",
      "startTime": 38.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、マネージャーの最初の仕事",
      "startTime": 41.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に撮って、写真SNSにアップするからさ\nは～い、そこで笑ってね～",
      "startTime": 49.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え、あ、俺も一緒に写るんですか？\nkanaさんはともかく俺がいる意味ありますかね！？",
      "startTime": 54.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "分かってないな～、スタッフと一緒に写って\n『仲良しチーム！』をアピールするのが重要なんだって",
      "startTime": 62.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょっと動かないでよ、ブレるじゃん\nあとさ～、その顔もうちょっとマシになんない？",
      "startTime": 69.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "無茶言わないで下さい！",
      "startTime": 74.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3166.666666699996,
          "startTime": 77.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、kanaさん\nちょっと仕事のことでご報告したいことが……",
      "startTime": 80.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "あ～もう、ムカつく！\nなんでkanaよりあいつらの方が上なわけ！？",
      "startTime": 85.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！？\nあの、すみません、俺何か失礼なこと言いました……",
      "startTime": 89.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "あ？　別にあんたのことじゃなくて\nSNS見てたら、ヤなもん見つけちゃっただけ",
      "startTime": 98.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……ま、またSNSですか\nそう言えばkanaさん、ネットでも人気ですもんね",
      "startTime": 105.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、みんなkanaに注目してるからさ～\n面白いネタ探すのも、いつも苦労してるんだから",
      "startTime": 113.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "認知度を上げるのもアイドルには重要ですもんね\n毎日、何年も投稿を続けられるだけで凄いことです",
      "startTime": 121.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "でしょ～！！\n{user}ってば、分かってるじゃん～！！",
      "startTime": 127.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "でもさ、最近凄くムカつくやつらがいてさ\n『マイペースでかたじけない』っていうんだけど",
      "startTime": 134.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、そのグループって……",
      "startTime": 137.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "kanaが新作コスメの話をしたら\nあっちも似たような写真アップするし",
      "startTime": 143.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "フルーツサンド食べた！　って書いたら\nあっちもオシャレなスイーツ食べてるし",
      "startTime": 147.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "こっちの真似しておいて\nkanaより『いいね』が多く付いたりしててさぁ！",
      "startTime": 151.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……でも、丸パクリって訳でもなさそうですし\nどうしようもないんじゃあ……",
      "startTime": 159.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "だから、あいつらが絶対に真似出来ないネタを\nぶっこんでやるの！！",
      "startTime": 165.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "あんたも手伝ってよね\nkanaのマネージャーなんでしょ！？",
      "startTime": 168.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "よっ……と\nどうよ、kanaってば体柔らかいでしょ",
      "startTime": 175.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "他の子達もよくストレッチしていますけど……\nここまで柔らかい人はなかなか……凄いですね",
      "startTime": 183.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん\nま～、柔軟性ないとステージじゃ動けないからね",
      "startTime": 189.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan022.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと、ぼさっとしてないで\nさっさと撮ってよね！？",
      "startTime": 196.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "え、えっと\n今のkanaさんの様子を撮るんですよね？",
      "startTime": 200.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_01-kan023.m4a",
